Title: New Air-Gap Attack Uses SATA Cable as an Antenna to Transfer Radio Signals
Description: Researchers demonstrated a new Air-Gap attack, dubbed SATAn, in which attackers can use SATA cable as a wireless antenna to transmit radio signals.
